ef="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb946">Vahrn</placeName><date when="1901-07-22" n="01">22. 7. 1901</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann, Richard</persName><placeName ref="#pmb44278">Pörtschach</placeName><date when="1901-07-23">23. 7. 1901</date></correspAction><correspContext><tei:ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann, Richard</tei:ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1901-07-10_01">Beer-Hofmann an Schnitzler, 10. 7. 1901</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1901-07-27_02">Beer-Hofmann an Schnitzler, 27. 7. 1901</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
